original_title: Osees - Live at the Henry Miller Library, Big Sur
overview: Recorded from dusk till dawn 2 at the gorgeous Henry Miller Library in Big Sur. Same killer crew, similar killer vibes. An enchanting pre-holiday evening to tell you that we miss and love you. Play it loud and have one on us. And keep your chin up for goodness sake. -JPD
title: Osees - Live at the Henry Miller Library, Big Sur
